FBIS4-15450 "drsov068_v_94014" FBIS-SOV-94-068 Daily Report 7 Apr 1994 Lithuania Voluntary Defense Force Chief of Staff Appointed Voluntary Defense Force Chief of Staff Appointed LD0704131994 Vilnius Radio Vilnius Network in Lithuanian 1200 GMT 7 Apr 94 LD0704131994 Vilnius Radio Vilnius Network Lithuanian BFN [Text] According to a decree of the president of Lithuania, Lieutenant Colonel Algirdas Pocius has been appointed chief of staff of the country's voluntary defense service.
